title: Ep. - 341 - HANNAH BERNER AND PAIGE DESORBO FROM SUMMER HOUSE CHRIS FARAH REVIEWS 90 DAY FIANCE
description:
Hannah Berner and Paige DeSorbo from Bravo’s Summer House talk about Hannah’s engagement, why everyone remains bikini ready despite eating snacks all day long, and the root of Hannah fighting with Kyle this season.

 

Chris Farah is a comedian, writer, and most devoted 90 Day Fiance fan. She explains what everyone has been missing this season, and why the series remains her favorite show.

 

 

 

Reality Life with Kate Casey
